34/* These variables control which messages are selected. */
35extern DLL_VARIABLE int more_than;
36extern DLL_VARIABLE int less_than;
37
38/* If true, use the first available translation.
39 If false, merge all available translations into one and fuzzy it. */
40extern DLL_VARIABLE bool use_first;
41
42/* If true, merge like msgcomm.
43 If false, merge like msgcat and msguniq. */
44extern DLL_VARIABLE bool msgcomm_mode;
45
46/* If true, omit the header entry.
47 If false, keep the header entry present in the input. */
48extern DLL_VARIABLE bool omit_header;
49
